NB. load lif file

NB. =========================================================
life_file_load=: 3 : 0
pat=. <'*.lif';'lif pattern file'
r=. filechooser 0;'load *.lif file';pat;PATH
if. 0=#r do. 0 return. end.
  PATH=: }:0 pick fpathname r
  dat=. readlif r
if. dat-:0 do. return. end.
setpattern dat
)

