NB. readlif - read a *.lif file
NB.
NB. form: readlif file
readlif=: 3 : 0
dat=. 'b' fread y
if. 0 e. ('#Life 1.05';'#N') e. dat do.
  info 'Not a Life 1.05 file' 
  0 return.
end.
buildlife dat
)
